data.description: DREAMY RARE ONE STORY 5 BEDROOM, TURN KEY, MOVE-IN READY! Located in the highly desired KB HOME enclaves, this stunning home is picture perfect! This fashionable residence captures the essence of its architectural heritage. Enjoy 5 bedrooms, 2 full baths designer interiors in an open modern floor plan with tons of upgrades, never represented more beautifully than in the following editorial photo spread.  The main communal living area divides the primary wing from the family area where you will find the 5 bedrooms.  A huge tool shed and kids tree house with slide and swings highlight the huge rear yard.  The yard has possible RV access.  Also, enjoy slab Corian upgraded granite counters including the stunning island chef kitchen with gourmet appliances.  Enjoy many upgrades including 2 inch faux wood blinds, oversized primary ensuite with ensuite, indoor laundry, RV accessable, and much more....sophistication in a country setting.  Unbeatable!!!!
